description:
Bloated by rampant debauchery and military indulgence, The first Great American Empire started its decline in the 21st century and was ended with the 22nd. One of the key data points that began the decline was the migration of law enforcement to a nationwide system called C.O.P - Confederacy of Police.  The powerful megacorporations declared themselves ouside of the law, resulting in a puppet government. 

Eventually wars left one-fifth of the planet radioactive, and destroying all but 5% of the fuel supply.  Forced to survive on solar power, America became California.  Deserting the northern hemisphere en masse, Russia, Canada and Europe flooded the west coast of the US, resulting in the United Californian Systems of America.   
Now the world is crammed into the lower half of the globe.  Hardship and corruption prevail.  Religion has made a power-grab and the result is "Vatican Quest" located in Colorado, presided over by Pope Innocent XLII.  The year is 2530.
name: Devil Reborn

description:
The world has suffered a nuclear holocaust and the destruction of OPEC nations.  The world’s major power supply had been severely crippled, finally forcing the adaption of alternative sources ofenergy, the most successful being solar power.  In a world dependent on the sun, a mass exodus of the world population began, with most traveling toward the equator.  The United States became the United Californian Systems of America.  The east coast megatropolis became a ghost town in the wake of this human migration.

After several hundred years, the world began to once again take on a more civilized structure, but the rising world order was subject to a mix of opportunistic religion and self indulgence.  the struggle for control of a fading America is now happening in the churches, as much as the boardrooms and chemically altered minds of the public.  Drugs are big business, and corporations and racing to find just the right mix that will provide the most happiness with the least side effects.

Frightened by the explosive and public return of Grendel, crooked Pope Innocent XLII organizes his forces in an attempt to capture the mysterious Devil and prevent the unavoidable public relations fallout that’s sure to follow.  There is talk of a new Inquisition, and Confederacy of Police Officer Pellon Cross is unsurprisingly on the Church’s side. Meanwhile, corporate investigator Orion Assante continues building his case against the church.
name: Devil At Large

description: The terrorist Eppy Thatcher is certain of one thing: God is hate!  He's also sure that God demands a sacrifice...and he's driven to provide God just what he's looking for.  In the meantime, Orion Assante's investigation is coming apart at the seams, thanks to the efforts of the Church's inquisitor and C.O.P officer Pellon Cross.
name: Devil's Tracks

description: Bold enough to appear during a televised mass and conduct a daylight attack upon the Church Bazaar, Grendel has been reborn. Meanwhile, Officer Pellon Cross is not doing much to hide his improper involvement in the Church's affairs. Orion Assante's inquest pushes ahead while Sister Aimee joyfully starts a new Inquisition.
name: Devils, Devils Everywhere

description: After staging another public and bloody attack on the Church Grendel escapes into the sewers. Pellon Cross confronts the Pope, learning of the Church's plan to build a super weapon that will bring world domination. Responding to Orion Assante's investigation, Cross disbands the board of the Deva Princes, thus weakening any hopes Assante has of exposing Pope Innocent's plan.
name: Devils Driven

description: Eppy Thatcher is still recovering from the wounds sustained in his battle with Pellon Cross at the Church Bazaar. He embraces the healing powers of Grendel, setting of another deadly psychedelic episode. Meanwhile, Pellon Cross continues to do the Church's bidding by pillaging a nuclear depot, unfortunately he loses most of his gear and strands himself in the Sahara...
name: Devil's Delusions

description: With Pellon Cross away on a mission, Grendel takes the opportunity to confront Pope Innocent. The resulting fight ends with the Pope's secret exposed, providing fodder for Grendel's next pirate broadcast. As Pope Innocent begins to lose control and his identity becomes known, Orion Assante begins his new life as an outlaw...
name: Devil Unveiled

description: Orion Assante and his team plot to disrupt the annual Palm Sunday television special with their own pirate broadcast...and succeed. Overcome with rage and the desire for revenge, Pope Innocent pushes for the completion of the tower in time for Easter Sunday. Meanwhile, Orion experiences tragedy in his family life.
name: Devil's Holiday

description: While Eppy Thatcher continued spreading his anti-Church rhetoric, C.O.P. Officer Pellon Cross was spreading vampirism. As Cross and Grendel finally come together in battle, it is clear that God and the Devil are finally meeting...and the end is coming.
name: Devil's Disclosure

description: It's Easter Sunday and both God and the Devil will rise again. The incredible conclusion of the 10 issue story arc of Grendel: God and the Devil.
name: Devils' Demise

description: 12-year-old Misaki is beginning school in Tokyo. Upon arriving in the city she spots a competition being broadcast called Angelic Layer - the latest high tech battle game fought by using dolls (Angels). Enchanted with one of the Angels she sees fighting, Misaki is inspired to create her own Angel and it leads her on an adventure that she never in her wildest dreams would have thought possible! Now Misaki has entered the tournament with her doll, Hikaru, and together they plan to take the sport by storm!
name: Vol. 1

description: Welcome to Angelic Layer, the sport of the future, in which players pit their robotic 'angels' against each other in nationwide tournaments. Misaki Suzuhara has just discovered the game, and she's already making a name for herself. After a tough loss in her first battle, she's ready to turn her luck around. Her next match: a one-on-one duel with Japanese pop star Ringo Seto. And on the horizon is a battle with the fearsome Fujisaki sisters, who will do anything to win. The odds are stacked against Misaki and her speed-type angel Hikaru, but with friends cheering in the stands and a mad scientist mentor watching her back, she just might stand a chance.
name: Vol. 2

description: It's time for the Angelic Layer regional finals in Kanto, Japan, and in honor of the occasion, an all-new fighting arena has been unveiled! For the first time ever, players must navigate their robotic Angels around an interactive 3-D environment filled with craggy peaks and smoky crevices. Misaki Suzuhara, the Angelic Layer prodigy who went from pretender-to-contender in her first day of competition, is the first unlucky player to fight in the new ring. Her opponent is the super-experienced Kaede Saitou, whose Angel, Blanche, has a wicked hyper-mode attack. Fortunately, Misaki's got a few new tricks of her own.
name: Vol. 3

description: Nobody thought Misaki Suzuhara would make it this far in the Angelic Layer tournament. After a rocky start and some less than honorable opponents, she's well on her way to victory. But her latest opponent is her most difficult yet. Ohjiro Mihara is called the Prince of the Layer, and for good reason. With his speed-type angel, Wizard, he's unstoppable. Has Misaki reached the end of the road?
name: Vol. 4

description: The Fujisaka sisters are back! Misaki Suzuhara, rising star on the Angelic Layer scene, has already bested the older sister, but now she must face Arisu, a mechanical genius with one thing on her mind - revenge. For this long-awaited grudge match an all-new layer is unveiled: a winter wonderland that can freeze an unsuspecting angel. Can Misaki's warm heart melt this cold competition and get her to the final battle? The battles get personal in the final volume of Angelic Layer. Fight on, Misaki!
name: Vol. 5

description:
Akari Mizunashi is a new arrival in the gorgeous Martian city of Neo-Venezia. She becomes a gondolier tour guide and begins her training to become an Undine, the most coveted job on Aqua. Follow Akari's adventures as she discovers the wonders of Aria in this prequel to the popular anime and manga series.

Chapter Titles

  • Navigation 01: The Water Planet
  • Navigation 02: The Guide on the Water
  • Navigation 03: The City Submerged
  • Navigation 04: The Kingdom of Cats
  • Navigation 05: The Hill of Hope
name: Vol. 1

description:
Akari has finished the first part of her training, and she is ready to start taking on passengers of her own, but her first customer is going to be a real challenge. Can Akari prove that she's up to the task? And what will happen when the president of Aria sets out on his own to prove to the company that he's useful? It's summer in Neo Venezia, and it's going to be a season full of lovely surprises!

Chapter Titles

  • Navigation 06: My First Customer
  • Navigation 07: It's Hard Being President!
  • Navigation 08: Night-light Bells
  • Navigation 09: Enter the Hero!
  • Navigation 10: Fireworks
  • Bonus Navigation: Colds and Pudding
name: Vol. 2

description: From a small lake nestled in a secluded forest far from the edge of town something strange emerged one day: Three young girls. The three girls, Shem, Hamu and Japheth, are sisters from another world. Equipped with magical powers, they are charged with saving all the creatures of Earth from becoming extinct. However, there is someone or something sinister trying to stop them. While saving our world from destruction, these sisters live like normal human girls: They go to school, work at a flower shop, hang around with friends and even fall in love...
name: Vol. 1

description: The adventures of Japheth, Hamu and Shem never end! The three sisters set out to save the sole survivor of the turtle world. Meanwhile, Japheth's relations with the "pretty" boy starts getting serious. Shellshock sets in once secrets of his identity unravel in a flash. Speaking about identities, the sisters discover the identity of the mysterious Cactus Three?!
name: Vol. 2

description: From a small lake nestled in a secluded forest far from the edge of town something strange emerged one day: three young girls. Shem, Ham and Japheth are sisters from another world. Equipped with their magical powers, they are charged with saving all the creatures of earth from becoming extinct. However, there is someone - or something - sinister trying to stop them. While saving our world from destruction, these sisters live like normal human girls: they go to school, work at a flower shop, hang around with friends and even fall in love!
name: Vol. 3

description: A Racing gang is causing chaos on Mumbai-Pune highway by robbing rich people during night and this gang is backed by some powerful people in Mumbai. Will Doga be able to solve this menace. First of 4 issues in Express Way Series.
name: Express Way

description: The shadow of Chucky has been hanging over Andy Barclay his entire life -- now more than ever... As Chucky dissects Andy's life bit-by-bit, his defenses get more weak with every moment. Can Andy resist becoming Chucky's new vessel? And through it all - what side is Doc John, the voodoo priest on?

Inez travels to her country's capital city to learn of her mission--a mission that will call upon her to bring back the guardian dragon that will protect her country's fragile peace from the demon-race that lurks in the shadows...

--------

The young orphan girl Inez has a special gift that allows her to communicate with all creatures. A great, unknown destiny awaits her -- Inez is the Chosen One! She travels to the country's captial, where Inez learns of her missionL she must bring back the Guardian Dragon that will protect her country's fragile peace from the demon-race, lurking withint the shadows.

Chapter Titles

  • Episode 1: Hundred Years' Show
  • Episode 2: The War of Black Blood
name: Vol. 1

description:
What if... love could last forever? In this touching, scary, campy and very funny anthology comprised of fully illustrated supernatural love stories, romance is eternal -- but not without a price! Featuring the best of Janet Hetherington's Eternal Romance series, plus a new story revealing the origin of Destine!

Introduction by Supernatural Law creator Batton Lash.

Stories in this collection:

  • "The Mummy's Boy"
  • The Ghost of New Year's Past"
  • "Destine's Scream Date!"
  • "Too Much at Stake!"
  • "Kiss of Death!"
  • "Till Death Do Us Part!"
  • "The Green-Eyed Monster!"
  • "Once Bitten, Twice Shy!"
  • "My Phantom Lover!"
  • "The Night Student"

Illustrated poem: "My Love is Like a Pepperoni Pizza"
name: Eternally Yours: Illustrated Stories of Eternal Romance

description: A predatory alien race is hunting the biggest trophy in the galaxy - Godzilla's head! They've tagged the injured lizard with a tracking device and are stalking him over land and sea in hopes of electrocuting him with a high-tech net. Will the green Goliath escape the aliens' bloodthirsty ritual, or will G-Force find Godzilla's fricasseed, headless carcass floating on top of Portland's Willamette River?!
name: Target: Godzilla! part 3

description: How much punishment can the King of the Monsters take, anyway? Godzilla has already survived several attacks by a race of fierce, alien hunters. Now he needs a little help from his friends from G-Force, or else it's certain extinction at the hands of the fiercest hunters in the galaxy!
name: Target: Godzilla! part 4

description: Godzilla's survived being poisoned by an obsessed scientist. He's even survived being hunted by a predatory alien race. But can the King of the Monsters survive the fall of Rome? An evil professor has created a time-traveling device with one sole purpose in mind: world domination! His plan? To capture Godzilla and use him to change the course of history! Will he succeed? Not if G-Force has anything to say about it!
name: Part 1

description: Professor Mason is a scientist with two very deadly weapons. The first is a time machine, which gives him access to the entire panorama of history. The second is the King of the Monsters, whom Mason is using to terrorize the past! It's now 1588, the year of the Spanish Armada's ill-fated attack on England. Unless G-Force - with a little help from William Shakespeare and Sir Francis Drake - can find Mason and stop Godzilla's rampage, all of history will be altered...and the world we know will cease to exist!
name: Part 2

description: Every school-child knows that the famous 1906 San Francisco earthquake was caused by...Godzilla? That may be how history is rewritten if the unstable Professor Mason puts his two new weapons to use, the first being a time machine and the second being the King of the Monsters! It's up to G-Force to head off Godzilla's destructive historical rampage - but can mere humans repair history once Godzilla has thoroughly trampled it?
name: Part 3

description: Three hundred years from now there is no war, no conflict - only peace and brotherhood for all mankind. That is, until Professor Mason and his time-traveling army show up with Godzilla in tow! Mason has come to rob the future in order to rule our present, and he's brought the King of the Monsters with him to make sure nobody says different. The current story arc comes to a cataclysmic conclusion as Godzilla goes wild in a world he never made!
name: Part 4

description: More monster action, more monster fun! Trying to locate Godzilla in the sea off the coast of Peru, G-Force instead runs across a path of destruction left by another gigantic monster, Burtannus! Things go from bad to worse when the Peruvian Air Force gets involved and from worse to horrible when Godzilla himself shows up! It's monster vs. monster with G-Force caught in the middle!
name: Turf War

description: Dr. Kagaku, the leader of G-Force, has created a device that is sure to stop Godzilla in his tracks. That's the good news. The bad news is, somebody must place the device, with pinpoint accuracy, on Godzilla himself! Ordinarily, this would be a dangerous job. But to attempt it while the King of the Monsters is in the midst of a destructive rampage is suicidal! Grab a rope and strap on your crampons, your mission is "To Climb the Highest Monster!"
name: To Climb The Highest Monster!

description: If rough water and the threat of shark attack aren't enough to keep Australian bathers out of the water, how about a 300-foot-tall, fire-breathing lizard? Godzilla has taken to sunning himself on one of Australia's most popular beaches, giving the army and G-Force cause for concern. But it's all just a prelude to a battle royal when the mad Dr. Yamazaki's giant crustacean monster sets its sights on the city of Sydney and Godzilla!
name: The Yamazaki Endowment

description: When an undersea volcano disturbs Godzilla's slumber, the King of the Monsters awakens to find himself among the dinosaurs and other savage creatures of the Mesozoic era. Godzilla's in monster paradise - until he encounters a marauding monster from space intent on driving the dinosaurs to an early extinction. It's a clash with reverberations that will be felt through the ages!
name: Thunder In The Past

description:
When special unit G-Force invites Professor Yoshiwara to study a dormant Godzilla, they discover she has more than studies in mind -- namely revenge for her parents' death in Tokyo forty years earlier! But can her specially formulated "Killer Bee" missile kill the King of Monsters?!

Godzilla returns in a thirteen-part series from Dark Horse! This special zero issue sets the stage for the mayhem to come, featuring a combination of new artwork recapping old continuity and a reprint of the 'zilla story from DHC #s 10 and 11. Sound the alarms! The King of Monsters is back!
name: Blast From the Past

description:
When a strange tomb is discovered in Egypt, Anubis, the Egyptian lord of death, awakens from his sleep of 5,000 years. Yearning to beat his rival Yugi, Kaiba acquires a mysterious card that may grant his greatest wish...but at what cost? Now, the magic and monsters are in the real world, and Yugi must duel Kaiba and Anubis to save the world from a new age of darkness! The ultimate shadow game begins now!

Never before released in America or Japan, the official ani-manga of Yu-Gi-Oh! The Movie brings the film to life with full-color art and sound effects!
name: Prologue; Duelists; The Pyramid of Light; Shining Dragon; Shining Nova

description:
The final piece to the Zenescope's Wonderland trilogy brings the powerful story of Alice's daughter, Calie Liddle, full circle. Calie's infant daughter was taken from her arms and brought into the realm of madness known as Wonderland. Now Calie must go back to the one place she has tried for so long to escape in order to rescue her baby. The moment of truth has arrived as the girl who became a woman sets out to become a hero.

This is the final chapter of the most intense, riveting and addictive comic book series you've read in years and this time around there may be no escape from Wonderland.

Collects Escape From Wonderland issues #0-6 and an issue #1 script book.
name: HC/TPB

volume.name: Grimm Fairy Tales: Escape From Wonderland

description: This issue focuses on the Sports Relief charity event and many celebrities feature in the comic strips.
name: Sport Relief
